&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI at BambooHR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;At BambooHR, we’re all about setting people free to do great work, and we believe AI is a powerful partner in that mission. We’re leaning into intelligent tools to streamline our workflows, giving us more time for high-impact innovation. We look for curious, forward-thinking people who are ready to explore how AI can elevate their work and help us reimagine the future of HR.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Job Duties:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Account Executive, you’ll be a vital part of our growth—building relationships, identifying client needs, and guiding prospects through the sales journey. From generating leads to closing deals, you’ll help businesses discover how BambooHR can transform their HR processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You Will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prospecting &amp;amp; Lead Generation:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify and qualify new business opportunities through outreach and networking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Pipeline Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain an organized pipeline and track progress using our CRM system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Needs:&lt;/strong&gt; Understand client needs and present tailored BambooHR solutions to solve their challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Work closely with cross-functional teams to move deals through the sales process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Negotiation &amp;amp; Closing:&lt;/strong&gt; Assist in negotiating deals and moving prospects to a close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Learning:&lt;/strong&gt; Stay informed about product updates and market trends to improve sales performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Need to Get the Job Done:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 1-2&amp;nbsp; years of sales experience, preferably in B2B or SaaS sales. Prospecting/cold calling experience is a plus.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Tools:&lt;/strong&gt; Familiarity with CRM systems (like Salesforce) and basic sales tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Goal-Oriented:&lt;/strong&gt; A track record of achieving or exceeding sales quotas. Your success in a quota-carrying sales role will demonstrate your ability to meet or surpass targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong verbal and written communication skills, including the ability to present product demos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive &amp;amp; Persistence:&lt;/strong&gt; A strong desire to succeed and the ability to manage objections and push through challenges.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teamwork:&lt;/strong&gt; Ability to collaborate with colleagues to achieve sales goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coachability:&lt;/strong&gt; Willingness to learn from feedback and improve your sales approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Focused:&lt;/strong&gt; Understanding of BambooHR’s value and ability to communicate this to clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organized:&lt;/strong&gt; Attention to detail and ability to manage multiple prospects at once.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Positive Attitude:&lt;/strong&gt; Energetic and enthusiastic, bringing a positive approach to the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why BambooHR?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uncapped Earnings:&lt;/strong&gt; Potential for unlimited commission based on your performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team-Oriented Culture:&lt;/strong&gt; A supportive and collaborative work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career Growth:&lt

