&lt;li&gt;Develop original campaign and brand concepts that translate strategic direction into clear, compelling creative expressions and deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and direct visual solutions across a range of channels and formats, including digital, web, social, paid media, video, presentation, lifecycle, events, and other campaign touchpoints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with creative leaders, writers, designers, motion creatives, video partners, marketers, and cross-functional stakeholders to develop integrated creative work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interpret briefs, business goals, audience insights, and campaign strategies into strong conceptual routes and executable creative systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the visual and conceptual development of projects from early exploration through refinement and final production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce work that balances originality, brand alignment, clarity, and effectiveness while maintaining a high bar for craft and detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explore multiple creative directions quickly and thoughtfully, using iteration to sharpen ideas and uncover the strongest solution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present concepts and creative rationale clearly and persuasively to peers, partners, and senior stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to and uphold the visual expression of the brand, helping define the territory the company seeks to own in the minds of its market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strong creative partnership and constructive feedback to peers and collaborators in support of better work across disciplines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on design, advertising, video, visual storytelling, and emerging creative methods, including AI-enabled tools and workflows, and apply them thoughtfully where they improve the work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support production and execution with close attention to consistency, quality, and fidelity to the original creative intent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help establish and model standards for concepting, craft, visual excellence, and creative problem-solving across the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
