&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in art direction, brand, campaign, advertising, or integrated creative roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong portfolio demonstrating conceptual range, visual excellence, and high-q

