rchitecture, deep knowledge of cloud tech, and competencies in creating a strategic vision, will be the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;popover-trigger-:r2d:&quot; class=&quot;chakra-text css-1j6t0d7&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;3pq19-8-0&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-text=&quot;true&quot;&gt;driving&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span id=&quot;popover-trigger-:r2h:&quot; class=&quot;chakra-text css-1j6t0d7&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;3pq19-10-0&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-text=&quot;true&quot;&gt;force&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;popover-trigger-:r2j:&quot; class=&quot;chakra-text css-bcri66&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;3pq19-11-0&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-text=&quot;true&quot;&gt; of BambooHR’s technology transformation, including the strategic integration and advancement of Artificial Intelligence (AI) initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
