&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll use quick digital navigation and problem-solving skills to answer questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We know people matter, and that is exactly why our Client Service Specialists strive every day to make magical moments with our clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A successful Client Service Specialist will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide world-class customer service via phone, email, and chat communications with clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uphold and contribute to a brand of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bamboohr.com/why-bamboohr/&quot;&gt;setting people free to do great work&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop an understanding of how information connects in BambooHR products to quickly navigate to the core of client issues&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn how to guide clients in BambooHR performance management, time-tracking, onboarding, and applicant-tracking systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quickly think on your feet to work through complex questions and come up with creative solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;During training, you&#39;ll spend at least 6 hours per day on the phone. After training, your schedule will include 4 hours of phone support and 4 hours of chat support each day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be proactive in working independently while also thriving in a team-based environment with other Client Service Specialists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep up to date on new features and products to maximize value for clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in upselling and customer retention activities, utilizing BambooHR strategies to enhance customer satisfaction and loyalty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do your best, focused work, from 9 am to 6 pm, Monday through Friday (no nights or weekends!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
