&lt;p&gt;The Knowledge Governance Specialist supports the creation, organization, and continuous improvement of customer-facing and internal knowledge within BambooHR’s Customer Experience organization. This role helps keep Help Center content, in-app guidance, internal SOPs, and AI-consumable knowledge (including chatbot responses, in-product guidance, and internal support tools) accurate, consistent, and easy for both employees and customers to use.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
